dm\_industrial (rev#FINAL), by warhawk3407
=========================================

Compilation settings :
----------------------
BSP  = "Normal" Vvis = "Normal" Vrad = "Normal" HDR = "ON" (the HDR was smoothed to be less violent)

Features :
----------
Map overview & RADAR (IMPROVED), SNOWFALL, FOG, WIND, 3D SKYBOX (reEDITED)! Advanced lighting (IMPROVED)! NAV file included, bots are now able to walk everywhere ! Cubemaps (reflects)! ADDED SOUNDSCAPES.

Map inspired by the gameplay of aim\_ag\_texture2, and by the design of cs\_office or cs\_assault. Havefun !

I have the project to create two new versions : one cs_ and a one de_ , so be patient :-p
